{"tid":2429780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本促中國停止對日本公民作肛拭子檢測　指「帶來極大心理痛苦」","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T14:04:11.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7fae58ffe8e133547c393b861b1542126ab413c2","tid":2429780,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/1_A0InU_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F1_A0InU_1200x0.png&h=7805c5ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本周一（1 日）表示，已要求中國停止對日本公民進行武漢肺炎（COVID-19）的肛門拭子檢測，稱有關程序為人帶來「極大心理痛苦」。<br />\n<br />\n中國自本年初開始，在部分出現疫情的社區採用肛拭子檢測，過程中，檢測人士須以膝胸臥位或側臥姿勢接受採樣，消毒棉拭子會插入檢測者肛門 3 至 5 厘米處，輕輕旋轉然後拔出。<br />\n<br />\n日本內閣官房長官加藤勝信周一在記者會上指，一些日本人向日本駐華大使館報告反映，曾接受肛拭子檢測，對他們造成極大心理痛苦。加藤又指，目前不清楚有多少日本公民曾接受該檢測，稱會不斷要求中國作出改變。他重申，肛門拭子檢測在全球其他任何地方都尚未被確認使用。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人汪文斌則在同日回應，指中方根據疫情形勢變化，按照相關法律法規、科學動態，調整相關防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n早前美國《華盛頓郵報》也曾報道，美方有駐華外交人員被要求接受肛拭子檢測。美國國務院發言人曾表示，評估所有合理選項以處理問題，本著《維也納外交關係公約》維護美國官員的尊嚴。其後中國外交部表示經核實，中方從未提出該要求。"},{"pid":"ddddd553a3a3d22a1b9ce447b5929a28006e494a","tid":2429780,"uid":212249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:00:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/日本促中國停止對日本公民作肛拭子檢測-指-帶來極大心理痛苦/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E4%BD%9C%E8%82%9B%E6%8B%AD%E5%AD%90%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E6%8C%87-%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E6%A5%B5%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=9eaf489d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E4%BD%9C%E8%82%9B%E6%8B%AD%E5%AD%90%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E6%8C%87-%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E6%A5%B5%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6%2F&h=fadb4064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/日本促中國停止對日本公民作肛拭子檢測-指-帶來極大心理痛苦/</a><br />\n<br />\n張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5703a33c18b057767f5815bc4ae4c83459b2e2","tid":2429780,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmyoedd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftmyoedd.gif&h=9e5fdba8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}